*Nisam* imao vremena da pročitam knjigu. (I didn't have time to read the book.)

*Nisam* izabrao najbolju opciju. (I didn't choose the best option.)

*Nisam* mogao da se setim. (I couldn't remember.)

*Nisam* imala snage da pričam. (I didn't have the strength to talk.)

*Nije* on imao pravo da tako postupi. (He didn't have the right to act like that.)

*Nismo* mogli da se dogovorimo. (We couldn't agree.)

*Nismo* dovoljno dobro razumeli. (We didn't understand well enough.)

*Nije* on dovoljno dobro shvatio. (He didn't understand well enough.)